            <p>He has also worked on cases involving cloud computing infrastructure, including service delivery architectures on platforms such as Amazon Web Services (AWS) and Google Cloud Platform (GCP). Dr. Lavian has hands-on experience designing and deploying cloud-based systems, having built cloud services on both AWS and GCP during his work at UC Berkeley's SkyDeck startups.</p>
